data.text:
Age: 22.

Hometown: Born in Houston and raised in Tulsa.

Education: University of Oklahoma senior, majoring in elementary education. Graduated from Jenks High School in 2001.

Family: Parents Tom Berry and Kay Berry, sister and brother-in-law Kim and Josiah Borgos, all of Tulsa.

Talent: Ballet en pointe. Has studied with OU's School of Dance.

Platform: Building intolerance of drunken driving.
